    .bordered-panel
        %p
            Bree Koziara, Ed.M. Harvard University and Founder of academic stratEDGEy has a passion for student development and over ten years of tutoring experience. Bree loves history and received straight As and top marks in every subject she instructs. Bree teaches 8th grade US History, AP World History, and AP United States History, offering AP History Summer Boot Camps, weekly group tutoring sessions, and AP Exam review programs.

        .service-item
            %h3.title
                U.S. History/Geography (8th grade)
            .description.row
